content: Won't stop crashing when trying to review practice exam answers.
Even after the update the database of questions is still outdated. None of the questions were on the actual test.
great app to prep for written, I like the study features where the questions have explanations and refrence.
Remembered all the questions and answers but when I took the test, only about 20 questions were word for word and the rest were worded differently.
needs to get 2019 update

Unfortunately I cannot recommend this product. I just took the Commercial Airplane written test and most of the questions I was asked weren't in this app. Of the ones that were at least similar, most had been rewritten so that the answers were different. Even the diagrams in the test supplement were different, and those are public information. I recommend going elsewhere for your test prep. Shepard worked great for my Instrument written. I wish I hadn't cheaped out on this one.
Great app

I think the tests are oddly airplane heavy for questions on a rotorcraft test prep. Additionally. I wish there was a way to save your test scores so you can see trends of improvement. Often I accidentally bump the back button when checking my mistakes on the grade portion of a test and there is no going back. Almost a waste of time taking a 100 question test. Still love how much it helps me because getting 75% on this app leads to me grtti by 80% and up on the actual written exams.

Would be better if i could pick the number of questions on the test mode so that when i just want to take a quick test i don't have to go through 100 questions while waiting at the bus stop. It seems too simple in some aspects and needs some control. Give a study mode that lets you practice multiple categories and lets you pick how many questions to do in a session.
You guys trying to make me fail, there's only 1 IFR question...
Some questions refer you to a figure to find an airport or obstruction but there is nothing there.

The aspects I don't like is that some of the information such as the chart references are incorrect. Also it would be really nice to annotate on the charts to figure out exactly which grid you're on. Plus the functionality is a bit limited (no history). All in all good random test generator!

Go through each section of questions individually then take the test of random generated questions after you have studied each section of questions in its entirety. I passed my commercial first try and during the oral my answers were often right out of this software. Study hard especially in your weak areas
Unos meses despues de haber comprado la app, simplemente dejó de funcionar, aclarenme algo, la compre o la alquilé?
The update in the questions is great but the white background is too bright. Please include a night mode that toggles to a black background.
Simple and reliable

For the price, it's okay! It's simple and reliable. I would be willing to pay a bit more for some more functionality though, such as progress tracking or saving a session. Having the entire database downloaded is great for travelers.
It is nice to have a portable thing to study while you stand around and got nothing to do. Answers are cool, but just not as much as detail for some books I have read.

Studying is much easier using a touchscreen as opposed to a mouse on a laptop but I've already bought my CFI prep ware book and activation code. Why can't I?? and when am I going to be able to activate this app by the code I already paid for so I don't have to pay for this twice?!?
The explanations are mediocre at best.  With about 50% re-iterating the answer with no explanation of substance.  Make the explanations meaningful and insightful and you've got a solid app.
1 star off for 1 issues: Can't save study sessions so it is needed to start all over aging evere time. Pls fix
Effective tool, great for anytime studying! Would be five stars if the option to save progress worked and fc issue when returning to app was fixed
Outstanding app. Easy to use when ur on the go. Makes it easier to prepare for the tests. Highly recomend.
